  "state": "open",
  "locked": false,
  "title": "fix: update sentry-cli to use sourcemaps upload command (v3.0.0 API)",
  "user": { "login": "konard", "id": 1431904, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1431904?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/konard", "html_url": "https://github.com/konard", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/konard/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/konard/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/konard/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/konard/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/konard/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/konard/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/konard/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/konard/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/konard/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false },
  "body": "## Summary\n\n- Updates `scripts/upload-sourcemaps.mjs` to use the new sentry-cli 3.0.0+ API\n- Adds comprehensive case study documentation in `docs/case-studies/issue-969/`\n\n## Problem\n\nThe release workflow was failing with:\n\n```\nerror: unrecognized subcommand 'files'\nUsage: sentry-cli releases [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>\n```\n\nThis error occurred because `sentry-cli` version 3.0.0 (released December 15, 2025) removed the `releases files` subcommand that was being used to upload source maps.\n\n## Root Cause\n\nThe script `scripts/upload-sourcemaps.mjs` was using deprecated command syntax:\n\n```javascript\n// OLD (broken)\nexecSync(`npx @sentry/cli releases files ${version} upload-sourcemaps ./src ...`);\n```\n\n## Solution\n\nUpdated to use the new sentry-cli 3.0.0+ API:\n\n```javascript\n// NEW (working)\nexecSync(`npx @sentry/cli sourcemaps upload ./src --release ${version} ...`);\n```\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [x] Script syntax check passes (`node --check scripts/upload-sourcemaps.mjs`)\n- [x] ESLint passes (`npm run lint`)\n- [x] Prettier formatting passes for modified files\n- [x] Sentry integration tests pass (`node tests/test-sentry.mjs`)\n- [x] Verified new command syntax is valid (`npx @sentry/cli sourcemaps upload --help`)\n- [ ] CI pipeline passes (pending - latest commits need CI trigger)\n\n## Note on CI\n\nThe CI for the latest commits (which fix the Prettier issue with CLAUDE.md) was not triggered due to workflow concurrency settings. A manual re-trigger or a new push may be needed to verify the complete fix.\n\n## References\n\n- [Sentry CLI Source Maps Upload Guide](https://docs.sentry.io/platforms/javascript/sourcemaps/uploading/cli/)\n- [sentry-cli 3.0.0 Changelog](https://github.com/getsentry/sentry-cli/releases)\n- [Issue #969](https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/issues/969)\n\n## Documentation\n\nAdded a detailed case study at `docs/case-studies/issue-969/README.md` with:\n- Timeline of events\n- Root cause analysis\n- Lessons learned\n- CI logs archive\n\nFixes #969\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)",
